{"tid":1935002,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"傳統泛民們 你哋好心就去功能組別玩啦","createTime":"2020-03-20T09:26:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T05:09:19.000Z","uid":89353,"like":36,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a27e1e05f7fe2e8105f192b93ad8269015eabec9","tid":1935002,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T09:26:56.000Z","msg":"坦白講 <span style=\"color: red;\">如果真正想贏到立法會</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">功能同地區都要<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">攞晒</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>傳統泛民資源多人多</strong><br />\n與其留喺地區同本土素人爭<br />\n最後搞到攬炒攞唔到議席<br />\n點解唔去功能組別<br />\n我哋搞咁多登記啊工會啊<br />\n如果功能組別冇代表我哋投咩<br />\n你哋有資源 叫人加入佢哋或者派人去功能一定比起本土素人去更加好<br />\n<br />\n再講講多句 功能組別啲咁嘅根本就係你地整出嚟<br />\n自己整出嚟嘅屎自己食返好合理姐<br />\n<br />\n如果大家同意既話<br />\n我希望大家一齊推到佢哋去功能組別為止<br />\n我哋要推要嗌功能組別會投佢地 但地區就一定唔會<br />\n唔可以留地區比佢哋<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">地區留本土 功能俾泛民<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"4185f21e490fd133dae327890ed514e6de1b5b02","tid":1935002,"uid":270307,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T09:28:56.000Z","msg":"P牌幫推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afc3e920da77c06ca21aecc6de6e444122b446b1","tid":1935002,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T09:37:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97b5f12036d9729e39e6610ce19733e6e4157612","tid":1935002,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T09:38:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a3bb037610aa1d690980834d02446fe247c1f7ed","tid":1935002,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-20T09:38